<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nicheng' Isu ka lunggil in ka hehpih deuhdeuh a,
 Amah chu ni eng sang inle a hawih ka sazaw ie;
 Amah chu keia di'n hawihna lopipen a hung hii,
 Nicheng'a ma sang in a hung hawih deuhdeuh zaw ta ie.

[V2]
 Akim le I he puou hi,
 Zie luipang apat hin;
 Aw, ziechun ama sang in,
 Hung hawihzaw deuh deuh ina.

[V3]
 2. Galkhat a ka et in A lopina chun ei salh hi,
 Lili pak hawih leh zingsawl sang inle A vak hawihzawi;
 Ka deihnate A hihdim in, A hihhawih deuhdeuh zawi,
 Nicheng' ama sang in a hung hawih deuhdeuh zaw ta ie.

[V4]
 3. Ka lungthim a hung chauh tiengleh Ama'n ei panpih a,
 Ka liengvaih laiin Ama'n A angsung ah ei pawm sek;
 Krista, ka gitloh cheng pawpa kha ka hehpih ahi,
 Nicheng'a ma sang in a hung hawih deuh deuh zaw ta ie.</lyrics>
<title>STILL SWEETER EVERY DAY</title>
<hymn_number>38</hymn_number>
</song>